ظآزHow beautifulظآز

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 8=

11
00:00:46,039 --> 00:00:46,520
Mei Lin,

12
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:47,679
are you okay?

13
00:00:48,359 --> 00:00:49,320
The physician said

14
00:00:49,960 --> 00:00:52,000
the dagger was laced with lethal poison.

15
00:00:52,399 --> 00:00:54,039
It paralyzes my legs.

16
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:55,520
In the end,

17
00:00:56,759 --> 00:00:57,759
it will take my life.

18
00:00:58,320 --> 00:01:02,320
I just wanted to see you one last time.

19
00:01:05,640 --> 00:01:06,439
Yiyi.

20
00:01:08,280 --> 00:01:09,079
(Yiyi!)

21
00:01:15,959 --> 00:01:17,879
(The dagger was laced
with lethal poison.)

22
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:19,560
(It paralyzes my legs.)

23
00:01:20,000 --> 00:01:20,799
Paralyze?

24
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:23,439
Could it be the same poison Jinghe had?

25
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:28,159
Don't be afraid. I have the cure.

26
00:01:28,480 --> 00:01:30,079
Even the Reaper

27
00:01:30,079 --> 00:01:32,799
cannot take you from me!

28
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:49,719
Mei Lin, here's the antidote!

29
00:01:49,760 --> 00:01:51,400
(Sorry, Prince Jinghe, we're ordered)

30
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,400
(not to let you in.)

31
00:01:53,799 --> 00:01:54,599
(Move aside!)

32
00:01:56,159 --> 00:01:57,439
I told you there are orders!

33
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:02,719
Jinghe,

34
00:02:03,079 --> 00:02:04,760
do you take my court for a marketplace?

35
00:02:05,840 --> 00:02:08,080
I was attacked by an assassin,

36
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:10,439
and you don't seem to care at all.

37
00:02:11,080 --> 00:02:12,560
Is it indifference

38
00:02:12,800 --> 00:02:16,520
or regret that I didn't die completely?

39
00:02:18,080 --> 00:02:19,560
You suspect me?

40
00:02:30,840 --> 00:02:33,120
(I can't waste
such a great opportunity.)

41
00:02:52,199 --> 00:02:53,000
(This mask...)

42
00:02:54,879 --> 00:02:56,520
(He's indeed the one I'm looking for.)

43
00:02:59,560 --> 00:03:02,159
A cripple who can't even
care for himself

44
00:03:02,240 --> 00:03:04,000
dares to come make trouble here?

45
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,360
You investigated me?

46
00:03:05,360 --> 00:03:07,280
With those crippled legs of yours?

47
00:03:08,240 --> 00:03:09,039
Your Highness!

48
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,039
Since your legs are already useless,

49
00:03:15,520 --> 00:03:17,719
you might as well lose your hands too.

50
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,520
Murong Jinghe, how dare you!

51
00:03:30,800 --> 00:03:32,919
Xuanlie, swords have no eyes.

52
00:03:33,199 --> 00:03:35,800
Who knows where the next one lands?

53
00:03:36,439 --> 00:03:37,240
Let's go.

54
00:04:03,120 --> 00:04:04,680
Your Highness, I...

55
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,520
You're fine now.

56
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:07,479
I already fed you the antidote.

57
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:08,879
You've been cured.

58
00:04:09,759 --> 00:04:10,719
I owe you so much.

59
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:12,479
I can't thank you enough.

60
00:04:13,639 --> 00:04:15,039
If you don't mind,

61
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,920
I'm willing to serve you

62
00:04:18,439 --> 00:04:19,480
as your Secondary Consort.

63
00:04:20,879 --> 00:04:21,920
Wonderful.

64
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,680
What Jinghe couldn't give you,

65
00:04:23,839 --> 00:04:25,279
I'll give you all of it.

66
00:04:29,399 --> 00:04:30,560
(The day we marry)

67
00:04:31,160 --> 00:04:32,639
(will be the day you die.)

68
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,079
Hurry, take the antidote.

69
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:49,000
How did it go?

70
00:04:50,920 --> 00:04:51,839
Everything went well.

71
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,560
I got the antidote
for the Bone-Erosion Powder.

72
00:04:55,439 --> 00:04:56,759
I've also confirmed

73
00:04:57,199 --> 00:05:00,279
Prince Xuanlie
is the head of the Shadow Bureau.

74
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:03,079
It's just that today,

75
00:05:04,240 --> 00:05:05,240
Murong Jinghe...

76
00:05:07,879 --> 00:05:10,160
He went to see Prince Xuanlie himself.

77
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,439
He was humiliated.

78
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:20,360
I wonder how he's doing.

79
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:23,639
Shiqi,

80
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:29,040
are you... worried about him?

81
00:05:51,740 --> 00:05:53,700
ظآزMoonlight spills like quiet tidesظآز

